               <head><persName ref="#eck" type="author"><forename>Andreae</forename>
                     <surname>Eck</surname>
                     <addName>ex <placeName ref="#gall">Sancto
                     Gallo</placeName></addName></persName> ad <persName ref="#vadi"
                        ><surname>Vadianum</surname>
                     <roleName>Praeceptorem</roleName></persName>.</head>
               <lg>
                  <l><placeName ref="#roma">Roma</placeName> suo merito gaudet celebrata <persName
                        ref="#verg">Marone</persName>,</l>
                  <l>Huius habent horum carmine gesta decus.</l>
                  <l>Sic de te, laudem modo si <persName ref="#vadi">Vadiane</persName> repones,</l>
                  <l>Gaudebit <placeName ref="#roma">Roma</placeName> gratior, <placeName
                        ref="#helv">Helvetia</placeName>.</l>
               </lg>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" corresp="#vadi_18">
               <head>&lt;Ein Gedicht&gt; von <persName ref="#eck"><forename>Andreas</forename>
                     <surname>Eck</surname>
                     <addName>aus Sankt Gallen</addName></persName> an seinen <persName ref="#vadi"
                        ><roleName>Lehrer</roleName>
                     <forename>Watt</forename></persName>.</head>
               <p><placeName ref="#roma">Rom</placeName>, das f체r seinen Verdienst gepriesen wurde,
                  freut sich 체ber <persName ref="#verg">Maro</persName>, durch dessen Lied haben
                  deren (sic!) Taten Zier. So wird sich die <placeName ref="#helv"
                     >Schweiz</placeName> 체ber dich, <persName ref="#vadi">Watt</persName>, freuen,
                  wenn du &lt;ihr&gt; Lob erstattest, dankbarer als <placeName ref="#roma"
                     >Rom</placeName>.</p>
